metadata.name: #DPLO - AAA Pass
metadata.description: The Project DJ - AAA Pass is a crossover between a mint pass and an all access membership to the Project DJ space. It not only contains early access to a FREE MINT of all future drops but it will also signify your belief in the Project. By purchasing this item you are signaling to the blockchain community that you are a larger part of the Project and ready to help it grow. You will be able to carry this pass around the metaverse with you for all-access to only the coolest musical events.
